        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-606",
        "content": "Well, he sat by his ice cool fire and thought about his journey to the earth, and finally he decided the only way he could get there was to slide down a moonbeam.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
