        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-606",
        "content": "It was cooked by the cook boys, and they ate thereof; though bad effects came upon all from it afterwards. Then began Thorhall, and said, \"Has it not been that the Redbeard has proved a better friend than your Christ?",
